This directory includes agents for transmitting and receiving FASGuard/STIX attack
reports and FASGuard/STIX rule transmitting/receiving as well as injecting rules
into a running Snort. The relevant Python code includes:

attackRcvD.py,attackXmitD.py - Attack report transmit and receive.
ruleRcvD.py,ruleXmitD.py - Rule transmit and receive.
RuleInjector.py - Sends signal to Suricata to cause rule re-loading.
